    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="域名-https-支持"><a href="#域名-https-支持" class="headerlink" title="域名 https 支持"></a>域名 https 支持</h3><blockquote><p>参考了 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/yucicheung/article/details/79560027" title="https://blog.csdn.net/yucicheung/article/details/79560027" target="_blank" rel="noopener">为Github page绑定自定义域名并实现https访问</a></p></blockquote><p>感谢 <a href="https://dash.cloudflare.com" title="https://dash.cloudflare.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CLOUDFLARE</a> 的免费服务。</p><p><strong>NOTE：</strong> 经过测试，设置后可以使用 https 和 http 来访问域名，但是默认使用 http。因此，为了域名可达，根目录中的 <code>_config.yml</code> 的 url 属性还是应该为 http 开头的。</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="设置网站背景"><a href="#设置网站背景" class="headerlink" title="设置网站背景"></a>设置网站背景</h3><p>首先，选择你的背景图片，放在根目录下的 <code>themes/next/source/images/background.jpg</code>。</p><p>然后，工程目录下的 <code>themes/next/source/css/_custom/coustom.styl</code> 文件添加代码:</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// Custom styles.</span><br><span class="line">@<span class="keyword">media</span> screen and (min-width:<span class="number">1200px</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="selector-tag">body</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">background-image</span>:<span class="built_in">url</span>(/images/background.jpg);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">background-repeat</span>: no-repeat;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">background-attachment</span>:fixed;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">background-position</span>:<span class="number">50%</span> <span class="number">50%</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">background-size</span>: cover;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="selector-id">#footer</span> <span class="selector-tag">a</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attribute">color</span>:<span class="number">#eee</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="评论功能：-valine"><a href="#评论功能：-valine" class="headerlink" title="评论功能： valine"></a>评论功能： valine</h3><blockquote><p>参考自 <a href="https://blog.csdn.net/blue_zy/article/details/79071414" title="https://blog.csdn.net/blue_zy/article/details/79071414" target="_blank" rel="noopener">为你的Hexo加上评论系统-Valine</a></p></blockquote><p><strong>NOTE：</strong> 注意 next 主题的 <code>_config.yml</code> 配置文件中是 <code>app_id</code> 还是 <code>appid</code>，<code>app_key</code> 还是 <code>appkey</code>，不同版本中不同。</p><h3 id="文章阅读统计：-leancloud"><a href="#文章阅读统计：-leancloud" class="headerlink" title="文章阅读统计： leancloud"></a>文章阅读统计： leancloud</h3><h3 id="添加-RSS-deprecated"><a href="#添加-RSS-deprecated" class="headerlink" title="添加 RSS [deprecated]"></a>添加 RSS [deprecated]</h3><blockquote><p>参考自 <a href="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000009544924" title="https://segmentfault.com/a/1190000009544924" target="_blank" rel="noopener">hexo的next主题个性化配置教程</a></p></blockquote><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2018/10/18/5bc877472fd9e.png" alt="微信图片_20181018200542.png"></p><p>首先，切换到根目录，安装 Hexo 插件 hexo-generator-feed：（会保存在 <code>node_modules</code> 文件夹）<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">$</span> npm install --save hexo-generator-feed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>接下来，进入根目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，<strong>添加</strong>：<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span> Extensions</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span># Plugins: http://hexo.io/plugins/</span><br><span class="line">plugins: hexo-generate-feed</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>然后，进入 themes/next 目录下的 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件，<strong>修改</strong>：<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Set rss to false to disable feed link.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Leave rss as empty to use site's feed link.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Set rss to specific value if you have burned your feed already.</span></span><br><span class="line">rss: /atom.xml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>配置完成后，重新生成一次（会在 ./public 文件夹中看到 atom.xml 文件）<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="搜索功能：-algolia-deprecated"><a href="#搜索功能：-algolia-deprecated" class="headerlink" title="搜索功能： algolia [deprecated]"></a>搜索功能： algolia [deprecated]</h3><blockquote><p>参考了 <a href="https://juejin.im/post/5af3f9d1518825673e35a6eb" title="https://juejin.im/post/5af3f9d1518825673e35a6eb" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo+Next集成Algolia搜索</a></p></blockquote><h3 id="其它优化参考"><a href="#其它优化参考" class="headerlink" title="其它优化参考"></a>其它优化参考</h3><ol><li><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/33616481" title="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/33616481" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo搭建的GitHub博客之优化大全</a></li></ol>]]></content>
    
